01:33:01.943 --> 01:33:04.712 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You know, the Security
Council finally got around

01:33:04.813 --> 01:33:06.247 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
