01:33:49.824 --> 01:33:50.792 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So let's support what
Secretary Kerry and the

01:33:50.892 --> 01:33:51.993 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
