let's hope that we can

01:33:52.093 --> 01:33:53.328 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
accelerate the cease-fire,
because I fear that the

01:33:53.428 --> 01:33:54.662 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Russians will continue
their bombing, try to do

01:33:54.762 --> 01:33:55.997 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
everything they can to
destroy what's left of the

01:33:56.097 --> 01:33:57.131 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
opposition.

01:33:57.232 --> 01:33:58.032 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And remember, the Russians
have not gone after ISIS

01:33:58.132 --> 01:33:59.367 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
or any of the other
terrorist groups.

01:33:59.467 --> 01:34:00.702 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
So as we get a
cease-fire and maybe some

01:34:00.802 --> 01:34:02.036 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
humanitarian corridors,
that still leaves the

01:34:02.136 --> 01:34:03.371 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
terrorist groups on the
doorstep of others in

01:34:03.471 --> 01:34:04.706 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Syria, Turkey, Lebanon,
Jordan, and the like.

01:34:04.806 --> 01:34:06.040 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
