work to do, and let's try

01:34:06.140 --> 01:34:07.475 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to make sure we actually
implement what has been

01:34:07.575 --> 01:34:08.142 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
agreed to with
the Russians.

01:34:08.243 --> 01:34:09.077 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

01:34:09.177 --> 01:34:10.245 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SANDERS: Let me just
-- just say this.

