a no-fly zone in Syria.

01:34:31.466 --> 01:34:36.437 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think you do have a
humanitarian tragedy

01:34:39.274 --> 01:34:46.014 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
there, as I mentioned
a moment ago.

01:34:46.114 --> 01:34:50.151 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I applaud Secretary Kerry
and the president for

01:34:50.251 --> 01:34:52.253 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
trying to put together
this agreement.

01:34:52.353 --> 01:34:57.358 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Let's hope that it holds.

01:35:06.901 --> 01:35:11.506 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SANDERS: But furthermore,
what we have got to do,

01:35:11.606 --> 01:35:14.475 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I'm sorry, yes, I do
believe that we have got

01:35:14.576 --> 01:35:17.445 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to do everything that
