01:35:19.581 --> 01:35:22.817 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But I do hope that in
years to come, just as

01:35:22.917 --> 01:35:26.187 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
