relations with Cuba.

01:35:29.490 --> 01:35:32.093 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And by the way, I hope we
can end the trade embargo

01:35:32.193 --> 01:35:33.728 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
with Cuba as well.

01:35:33.828 --> 01:35:38.099 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But the idea that we some
day maybe have decent

01:35:38.199 --> 01:35:41.970 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
