01:35:44.906 --> 01:35:46.708 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
world, yes, that is
something I want to

01:35:46.808 --> 01:35:47.475 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
achieve.

01:35:48.009 --> 01:35:50.278 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I believe that the
best way to do that is to

01:35:50.378 --> 01:35:53.448 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
be aggressive, to be
principled, but to have

01:35:53.548 --> 01:35:56.718 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the goal of trying
to improve relations.

01:35:56.818 --> 01:35:59.220 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That's how you make
peace in the world.

01:35:59.320 --> 01:36:01.956 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You sit down and you work
with people, you make

01:36:02.056 --> 01:36:07.195 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
demands of people, in this
case demanding Iran stop

01:36:07.295 --> 01:36:09.330 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
the support of
international terrorism.

01:36:09.430 --> 01:36:10.264 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

01:36:10.365 --> 01:36:12.400 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
CLINTON: Well, I
respectfully disagree.

01:36:12.500 --> 01:36:16.571 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think we have achieved
a great deal with the

01:36:16.671 --> 01:36:19.207 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
