under the agreement.

01:36:31.219 --> 01:36:33.688 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I do not think we should
promise or even look

01:36:33.788 --> 01:36:35.757 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
