to get done with Iran.

01:36:38.626 --> 01:36:40.928 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Yes, they have to stop
being the main state

01:36:41.029 --> 01:36:42.430 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
sponsor of terrorism.

01:36:42.530 --> 01:36:44.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Yes, they have to stop
trying to destabilize the

01:36:45.066 --> 01:36:47.235 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
