even more chaos.

01:36:47.568 --> 01:36:49.537 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Yes, they've got to
get out of Syria.

01:36:49.637 --> 01:36:52.073 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They've got to quit
sponsoring Hezbollah and

01:36:52.173 --> 01:36:53.141 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Hamas.

01:36:53.241 --> 01:36:54.475 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They have got to quit
trying to ship rockets

01:36:54.575 --> 01:36:56.544 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
