used against Israel.

01:36:56.744 --> 01:36:58.813 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We have a lot of work to
do with Iran before we

01:36:58.913 --> 01:37:01.749 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
