move toward normalized

01:37:01.849 --> 01:37:02.817 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
relations with us.

01:37:02.917 --> 01:37:03.751 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

01:37:03.851 --> 01:37:06.621 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SANDERS: We have a
lot of work to do.

01:37:06.721 --> 01:37:08.222 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
We have a lot
of work to do.

01:37:08.322 --> 01:37:10.692 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
But I recall when
Secretary Clinton ran

01:37:10.792 --> 01:37:14.095 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
