01:37:20.802 --> 01:37:22.503 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Of course you are right.

01:37:22.603 --> 01:37:25.339 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Iran is sponsoring
terrorism in many parts of

01:37:25.440 --> 01:37:27.108 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
