destabilizing areas.

01:37:27.208 --> 01:37:28.676 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Everybody knows that.

01:37:28.776 --> 01:37:33.081 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But our goal is, in fact,
to try over a period of

01:37:33.181 --> 01:37:37.618 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
time to, in fact, deal
with our enemies, not just

01:37:37.719 --> 01:37:38.553 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ignore that reality.

