CLINTON: ... Senator
Sanders, from a debate in

01:37:40.788 --> 01:37:43.324 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
2008, quote what I said.

01:37:43.424 --> 01:37:47.261 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
