without conditions.

01:37:54.869 --> 01:37:58.272 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That is the appropriate
approach in order to get

01:37:58.372 --> 01:38:00.575 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
