to your friends.

01:38:12.420 --> 01:38:14.021 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's harder to talk
to your enemies.

01:38:14.122 --> 01:38:14.922 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think we should do both.

01:38:15.022 --> 01:38:15.590 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

01:38:15.690 --> 01:38:16.758 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
IFILL: Let me move on.

01:38:16.858 --> 01:38:20.261 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You have both mentioned
the humanitarian tragedies

01:38:20.361 --> 01:38:21.729 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
which have been an
outgrowth in part of what

01:38:21.829 --> 01:38:23.097 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
