01:38:23.197 --> 01:38:24.999 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
More than a million
refugees entered Europe in

01:38:25.099 --> 01:38:26.167 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
2015.

01:38:26.267 --> 01:38:30.071 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Another 76,000 just last
month, that is about 2,000

01:38:30.171 --> 01:38:31.873 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
