01:38:32.306 --> 01:38:35.643 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Nearly 400 people have
been lost at sea so far

01:38:35.743 --> 01:38:37.678 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
