world, where should the

01:38:44.318 --> 01:38:44.886 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
U.S.

01:38:44.986 --> 01:38:46.020 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
be on this?

01:38:46.120 --> 01:38:48.356 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
What should the United
States be doing, Secretary

01:38:48.456 --> 01:38:49.290 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Clinton?

01:38:49.390 --> 01:38:50.658 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
CLINTON: Well, I was
pleased that NATO

01:38:50.758 --> 01:38:52.927 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
