01:39:30.264 --> 01:39:33.734 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
from intelligence and
other sources that they

01:39:33.835 --> 01:39:36.971 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
can come to our country,
we should be doing our

01:39:37.071 --> 01:39:38.072 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
part.

01:39:38.172 --> 01:39:40.508 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And we should back up the
recent donors conference

01:39:40.608 --> 01:39:43.878 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to make sure we have made
our contribution to try to

01:39:43.978 --> 01:39:48.749 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
