description of it.

01:40:00.695 --> 01:40:03.297 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So we do as the United
States have to support our

01:40:03.397 --> 01:40:06.067 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
