allies in Europe.

01:40:06.167 --> 01:40:07.401 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
We have to
stand with them.

01:40:07.501 --> 01:40:10.037 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We have to provide
financial support to them.

01:40:10.137 --> 01:40:13.307 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We have to provide the
NATO support to back up

01:40:13.407 --> 01:40:14.575 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
the mission that
is going on.

01:40:14.675 --> 01:40:17.511 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And we have to take
properly vetted refugees

01:40:17.612 --> 01:40:18.713 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ourselves.

01:40:18.813 --> 01:40:21.549 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SANDERS: A couple of years
ago, I had the opportunity

01:40:21.649 --> 01:40:24.986 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
