reasonable housing and

01:40:44.805 --> 01:40:46.807 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
conditions for
those people.

01:40:47.975 --> 01:40:52.813 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It seems to me that given
our history as a nation

01:40:52.914 --> 01:40:56.584 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
that has been a beacon of
hope for the oppressed,

01:40:56.684 --> 01:41:00.922 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
for the downtrodden, that
I very strongly disagree

01:41:01.022 --> 01:41:02.890 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
with those Republican
candidates who say, you

01:41:02.990 --> 01:41:06.260 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
