their home with nothing,

01:41:09.664 --> 01:41:10.765 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
nothing at all.

01:41:10.865 --> 01:41:13.334 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That is not what America
is supposed to be about.

01:41:13.901 --> 01:41:17.004 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So I believe that working
with Europe -- and, by the

01:41:17.104 --> 01:41:19.407 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
way, you know, we've
got some very wealthy

01:41:19.507 --> 01:41:21.776 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
