responsibility, as well.

01:41:28.849 --> 01:41:32.586 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But I think this is a
worldwide -- that the

01:41:32.687 --> 01:41:36.490 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
