01:41:56.877 --> 01:42:00.314 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He's a 40-year-old
stay-at-home dad in Dover,

01:42:00.414 --> 01:42:01.482 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
