01:42:03.351 --> 01:42:05.119 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
the course of
human history.

01:42:05.219 --> 01:42:08.456 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Can you name two leaders
-- one American and one

01:42:08.556 --> 01:42:11.025 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
