nothing that we could not

01:43:28.736 --> 01:43:29.403 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
accomplish.

01:43:30.137 --> 01:43:32.873 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And kind of -- that's
what I see our campaign is

01:43:32.973 --> 01:43:34.508 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
about right now.

01:43:34.608 --> 01:43:38.112 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
In this particular moment
of serious crises, saying

01:43:38.212 --> 01:43:40.548 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to the American people
don't give up on the

01:43:40.648 --> 01:43:41.849 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
