01:43:41.949 --> 01:43:44.285 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
don't listen to the Trumps
of the world and allowing

01:43:44.385 --> 01:43:45.719 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
them to divide us.

01:43:45.820 --> 01:43:50.124 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
If we reengage and get
involved, yeah, we can

01:43:50.224 --> 01:43:53.828 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
