01:44:00.267 --> 01:44:02.970 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
In the same light, as the
foreign leader, Winston

01:44:03.070 --> 01:44:05.306 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Churchill's politics
were not my politics.

01:44:05.406 --> 01:44:07.441 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
He was kind of a
conservative guy in many

01:44:07.541 --> 01:44:08.542 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
