juggernaut and rallied

01:44:20.187 --> 01:44:23.190 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
them and eventually won
an extraordinary victory.

01:44:23.290 --> 01:44:25.092 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Those are two leaders
