01:45:49.944 --> 01:45:52.346 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
CLINTON: ... put us on
firm ground, and has sent

01:45:52.446 --> 01:45:53.681 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
